Hard reuse and soft reuse
Concerning hard reuse, the median of the percentage of imported entities
(per i) is 0%, whereas its third quartile is 6.161%. That is, more than a
half of the ontologies that reuse others do not import any entity, and more
than 3/4 import, at most, a 6% of their entities.
